{"type":"text","timestamp":1782536325249,"sessionID":"ses_0f88ea0d8ffeABtVVgM5lrUMXi","part":{"id":"prt_f0771a686001H81WcdbupNEDDI","messageID":"msg_f07719e2e001rH5YvFvNMZfe1V","sessionID":"ses_0f88ea0d8ffeABtVVgM5lrUMXi","type":"text","text":"The group is narrowed to four rows under `build.gradle.kts` and `settings.gradle.kts`; three are already closed, and the remaining blocker is the `settings.gradle.kts` preferences/settings row still marked `planned`. Next I’m checking the source and the exact authority row plus the mapped target endpoints to either implement the missing coverage or close it with precise evidence.","time":{"start":1782536316550,"end":1782536325248}}}
